The paper deals with medical image analysis and machine learning, specifically using LSTMs for multi-label classification of chest x-rays. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the need to extract clinically relevant features and proposes alternative evaluation metrics, which are topics commonly associated with artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
